Graffiti and Paint Party
Dustin Moskovitz was invited
Holy Crap. This will be the best party you have EVER been to. Yeah, I said it. Bold? Maybe. But when have I not backed up something I've said? We are having a massive paint party. Our house is being knocked down in September by our landlord and we have permission to do whatever we want with our walls. So we are inviting all of our friends to come and paint the hell out of our walls. We will also have 12-15 artists, including graffiti artists and muralists painting along with you. There won't be ONE inch of white left on the walls. We will be shooting a short film to show the transformation of the spaces that you will be able to see online a couple weeks after the party. This is a party you're not going to want to miss! Please RSVP to me, and tell me how many you are bringing. We can only fit so many people in the house! No cover charge--we were originally collaborating with someone for a fundraiser, but no longer. Just bring yourself, and if you are really awesome, bring a 6 pack with ya! Beer/Wine/Music/LA's best Graffiti artists/community walls and AWESOME PEOPLE! See you Saturday! -Steve
